    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><!-- 发布状态: 是 --><!-- 文章ID: MTU1OTQ1NzA0OA== --><ul><li>标题: <code>记录Vim配置</code></li><li>分类: <code>其他</code></li><li>标签: <code>vim</code></li><li>创建时间: <code>2019-06-02</code></li><li>简介: <code>记录Vim配置</code></li></ul><hr><h2 id="记录vim配置"><a href="#记录vim配置" class="headerlink" title="记录vim配置"></a>记录vim配置</h2><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs vim"><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> nocompatible<br><span class="hljs-keyword">filetype</span> plugin <span class="hljs-built_in">indent</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">on</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; ========================== 插件地址开始 ==========================</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">exists</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;*minpac#init&#x27;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#init()<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#add(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;k-takata/minpac&#x27;</span>, &#123;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;type&#x27;</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;opt&#x27;</span>&#125;)<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#add(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Yggdroot/LeaderF&#x27;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#add(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Yggdroot/indentLine&#x27;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#add(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;vim-airline/vim-airline&#x27;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#add(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;vim-airline/vim-airline-themes&#x27;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#add(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;mileszs/ack.vim&#x27;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#add(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;dracula/vim&#x27;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#add(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;dense-analysis/ale&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">endif</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">has</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;eval&#x27;</span>)<br>    command! PackUpdate packadd minpac | <span class="hljs-keyword">source</span> $MYVIMRC | <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#update(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>, &#123;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;do&#x27;</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;call minpac#status()&#x27;</span>&#125;)<br>    command! PackClean  packadd minpac | <span class="hljs-keyword">source</span> $MYVIMRC | <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#clean()<br>    command! PackStatus packadd minpac | <span class="hljs-keyword">source</span> $MYVIMRC | <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> minpac#status()<br><span class="hljs-keyword">endif</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; ========================== 插件地址结束 ==========================</span><br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; ========================== 插件设置开始 ==========================</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; ===== ale 设置开始</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">g:ale_sign_column_always</span> = <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">g:ale_set_highlights</span> = <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">g:ale_sign_error</span> = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;✗&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">g:ale_sign_warning</span> = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;⚡&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">g:ale_statusline_format</span> = [<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;✗ %d&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;⚡ %d&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;✔ OK&#x27;</span>]<br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">g:ale_echo_msg_error_str</span> = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;E&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">g:ale_echo_msg_warning_str</span> = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;W&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">g:ale_echo_msg_format</span> = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;[%linter%] %s [%severity%]&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nmap</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">sp</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;Plug&gt;</span>(ale_previous_wrap)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">nmap</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">sn</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;Plug&gt;</span>(ale_next_wrap)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">nmap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;Leader&gt;</span>s :ALEToggle<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;silent&gt;</span> &lt;C-\&gt; :ALEDetail<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">s:error_symbol</span> = <span class="hljs-built_in">get</span>(g:, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;airline#extensions#ale#error_symbol&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;✗ &#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">s:warning_symbol</span> = <span class="hljs-built_in">get</span>(g:, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;airline#extensions#ale#warning_symbol&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;⚡ &#x27;</span>)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; ===== indentLine 设置开始</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">g:indentLine_char_list</span> = [<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;|&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;¦&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;┆&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;┊&#x27;</span>]<br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">g:indentLine_enabled</span> = <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-variable">g:indentLine_color_gui</span> = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;#7D8535&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; ===== indentLine 设置结束</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; ========================== 插件设置结束 ==========================</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; ========================== 功能设置开始 ==========================</span><br>packadd! dracula<br><span class="hljs-keyword">syntax</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">on</span><br>color dracula<br><span class="hljs-keyword">colorscheme</span> dracula<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> guifont=InconsolataGo:h16   <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 字体、字号</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> nofoldenable                <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 默认关闭代码折叠</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> backspace=<span class="hljs-built_in">indent</span>,eol,start  <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 智能回删</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> whichwrap+=h,<span class="hljs-keyword">l</span>,&lt;,&gt;,[,]      <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 光标循环</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> virtualedit=block,onemore   <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 允许光标出现在最后一个字符的后面</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">number</span>                      <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 设置行号</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> relativenumber              <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 显示相对行号</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> cursorline                  <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 突出显示当前行</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> cursorcolumn                <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 突出显示当前列</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> laststatus=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>                <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 永远显示状态栏</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> scrolloff=<span class="hljs-number">5</span>                 <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 屏幕顶/底部保持 5 行文本</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> ruler                       <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 总是在窗口右下角显示光标的位置</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> showcmd                     <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 显示输入的命令</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> mouse=<span class="hljs-keyword">a</span>                     <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 禁用鼠标(a为启用)</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> autoread                    <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 当文件在外部被修改，自动更新该文件</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> showtabline=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>               <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 设置一直显示标签</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">shiftwidth</span>=<span class="hljs-number">4</span>                <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 自动缩进单位</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> tabstop=<span class="hljs-number">4</span>                   <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; Tab 缩进单位</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> expandtab                   <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; Tab 替换为空格</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> noimdisable                 <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; Vim 会在离开 Insert 模式时自动切换至英文输入法</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> clipboard+=unnamed          <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 共享剪贴板</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> ignorecase smartcase        <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 搜索时忽略大小写，但在有一个或以上大写字母时仍保持对大小写敏感</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> incsearch                   <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 输入搜索内容时就显示搜索结果</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> hlsearch                    <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 搜索时高亮显示被找到的文本</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> nobackup                    <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 不生成临时文件</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> noswapfile                  <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 不生成 swap 文件</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> nowrap                      <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 禁止折行</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> wildmenu                    <span class="hljs-comment">&quot; Vim 命令行提示</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; ========================== 功能设置结束 ==========================</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; ========================== 自定义映射开始 ==========================</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;silent&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-s&gt;</span> :<span class="hljs-keyword">w</span><span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;silent&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;F2&gt;</span> :<span class="hljs-keyword">tabp</span><span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;silent&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;F3&gt;</span> :<span class="hljs-keyword">tabn</span><span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;silent&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-p&gt;</span> :LeaderfFile<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; nnoremap &lt;silent&gt; &lt;C-m&gt; :LeaderfMru&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;Leader&gt;</span>ff :Files<br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; ========================== 自定义映射结束 ==========================</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
