  <entry>
    <title>Mac上配置Jenkins为Unity导出AAR、APK</title>
    <link href="/65441edfbd02/"/>
    <url>/65441edfbd02/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><!-- 发布状态: 是 --><!-- 文章ID: 1603036800 --><ul><li>标题: <code>Mac上配置Jenkins为Unity导出AAR、APK</code></li><li>分类: <code>Unity</code></li><li>标签: <code>Jenkins</code> | <code>AAR</code> | <code>APK</code></li><li>创建时间: <code>2020-10-19</code></li><li>简介: <code>在Mac上通过配置Jenkins为来为Unity工程导出AAR，并且通过Jenkins导出APK</code></li></ul><hr><h1 id="Mac上配置Jenkins为Unity导出AAR打包APK"><a href="#Mac上配置Jenkins为Unity导出AAR打包APK" class="headerlink" title="Mac上配置Jenkins为Unity导出AAR打包APK"></a>Mac上配置Jenkins为Unity导出AAR打包APK</h1><blockquote><p>最终要达到的效果是 使用Jenkins导出AAR，并且导出APk，其中app中主要的功能为在已有Android中调用AAR，使Andorid原生与Unity的Activity切换。</p></blockquote><p>最终效果</p><p><img src="/../res/2020-10-19-Mac%E4%B8%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEJenkins%E4%B8%BAUnity%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BAAAR%E3%80%81APK/0.gif"></p><h2 id="为Mac安装、配置Jenkins"><a href="#为Mac安装、配置Jenkins" class="headerlink" title="为Mac安装、配置Jenkins"></a>为Mac安装、配置Jenkins</h2><h3 id="下载启动-Jenkins"><a href="#下载启动-Jenkins" class="headerlink" title="下载启动 Jenkins"></a>下载启动 Jenkins</h3><blockquote><p>官网上描述推荐使用<code>Homebrew</code>来安装。因此这篇笔记使用的<code>Homebrew</code>来安装。</p></blockquote><ol><li><del>使用该命令安装最新版本 <code>brew install jenkins-lts</code>，也可以在指定版本号来安装<code>brew install jenkins-lts@YOUR_VERSION</code>（下载太慢了）</del></li><li>改为使用war包通过Java来启动<code>java -jar jenkins.war --ajp13Port=-1 --httpPort=8080</code> 在在浏览器输入<code>http://localhost:8080</code>来访问。</li></ol><h3 id="首次启动-Jenkins"><a href="#首次启动-Jenkins" class="headerlink" title="首次启动 Jenkins"></a>首次启动 Jenkins</h3><ol><li>安装会遇到提示 “解锁Jenkins” 这里再终端使用<code>cat /Users/sszyc8/.jenkins/secrets/initialAdminPassword</code>来查看密码。</li><li>选择插件安装，这里了选择<code>安装推荐的插件</code>进行下一步操作，等待完成。</li><li>创建一个管理员账号。</li><li>配置完成进入到主界面，至此Jenkins安装配置结束。</li></ol><p><img src="/../res/2020-10-19-Mac%E4%B8%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEJenkins%E4%B8%BAUnity%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BAAAR%E3%80%81APK/1.png"></p><h2 id="创建一个用于测试的Unity工程"><a href="#创建一个用于测试的Unity工程" class="headerlink" title="创建一个用于测试的Unity工程"></a>创建一个用于测试的Unity工程</h2><h3 id="UI布局图"><a href="#UI布局图" class="headerlink" title="UI布局图"></a>UI布局图</h3><p><img src="/../res/2020-10-19-Mac%E4%B8%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEJenkins%E4%B8%BAUnity%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BAAAR%E3%80%81APK/2.png"></p><h3 id="编写Edior扩展来导出Andorid项目"><a href="#编写Edior扩展来导出Andorid项目" class="headerlink" title="编写Edior扩展来导出Andorid项目"></a>编写Edior扩展来导出Andorid项目</h3><p>示例：</p><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs go">using System;<br>using System.IO;<br>using UnityEditor;<br><br>public class BuildEditor<br>&#123;<br>    private static <span class="hljs-type">string</span> releasePath = Environment.CurrentDirectory + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;/Release/AndroidRelease&quot;</span>;<br><br>    [MenuItem(@<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Build/Export Android Project&quot;</span>)]<br>    private static void RunBuildAndroid()<br>    &#123;<br>        BuildAndroid();<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// Jenkins调用</span><br>    public static void JenkinsBuildAndroid()<br>    &#123;<br>        BuildAndroid();<br>    &#125;<br><br>    private static void BuildAndroid() &#123;<br>        EditorUserBuildSettings.SwitchActiveBuildTarget(BuildTargetGroup.Android, BuildTarget.Android);<br>        EditorUserBuildSettings.androidBuildType = AndroidBuildType.Release;<br>        EditorUserBuildSettings.androidBuildSystem = AndroidBuildSystem.Gradle;<br>        EditorUserBuildSettings.exportAsGoogleAndroidProject = <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>        PlayerSettings.defaultInterfaceOrientation = UIOrientation.Portrait;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">string</span>[] scenes = &#123; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Assets/Scenes/SampleScene.unity&quot;</span> &#125;;<br><br>        FileUtil.DeleteFileOrDirectory(releasePath);<br>        Directory.CreateDirectory(releasePath);<br><br>        BuildPipeline.BuildPlayer(scenes, releasePath, BuildTarget.Android, BuildOptions.AcceptExternalModificationsToPlayer);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>到此不出意外的话通过菜单栏<code>Build/Export Android Project</code>可以导出一个Android工程，这个Andorid工程路径就在<code>Unity工程/Release/AndroidRelease/</code>路径下。</p><blockquote><p>注意：因为目标是通过已有的Android工程切换到导出的AAR中Activity，Unity导出的Andorid工程中<code>AndroidManifest.xml</code>里指名了主activity的启动，所以我们需要使用自定<code>AndroidManifest.xml</code>，将表示作为主activity启动的代码代码清掉，得到下面这段<code>AndroidManifest.xml </code></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;?xml version=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;1.0&quot;</span> encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>?&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- GENERATED BY UNITY. REMOVE THIS COMMENT TO PREVENT OVERWRITING WHEN EXPORTING AGAIN--&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">manifest</span> <span class="hljs-attr">xmlns:android</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">package</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.unity3d.player&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">xmlns:tools</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;http://schemas.android.com/tools&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">application</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:isGame</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">activity</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;com.unity3d.player.UnityPlayerActivity&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:theme</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@style/UnityThemeSelector&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:screenOrientation</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;portrait&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:launchMode</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;singleTask&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:configChanges</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;mcc|mnc|locale|touchscreen|keyboard|keyboardHidden|navigation|orientation|screenLayout|uiMode|screenSize|smallestScreenSize|fontScale|layoutDirection|density&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:hardwareAccelerated</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;false&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">meta-data</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;unityplayer.UnityActivity&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">activity</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">application</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">manifest</span>&gt;</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至此，基于测试的Unity工程就完成了，将它传到Git上，接下来配置Jenkins。</p><h2 id="Jenkins配置自动打包工作流AAR"><a href="#Jenkins配置自动打包工作流AAR" class="headerlink" title="Jenkins配置自动打包工作流AAR"></a>Jenkins配置自动打包工作流AAR</h2><h3 id="先配置通过Jenkins导出Unity-AAR。"><a href="#先配置通过Jenkins导出Unity-AAR。" class="headerlink" title="先配置通过Jenkins导出Unity AAR。"></a>先配置通过Jenkins导出Unity AAR。</h3><h4 id="新建一个工作流"><a href="#新建一个工作流" class="headerlink" title="新建一个工作流"></a>新建一个工作流</h4><ol><li>从左侧侧边栏中选择<code>新建Item</code>。</li><li>输入工作流名称。</li><li>这里我们选择<code>Freestyle project</code>。</li><li>最后 确定 完成。</li></ol><p><img src="/../res/2020-10-19-Mac%E4%B8%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEJenkins%E4%B8%BAUnity%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BAAAR%E3%80%81APK/3.png"></p><h4 id="配置工作流"><a href="#配置工作流" class="headerlink" title="配置工作流"></a>配置工作流</h4><p>1、General选项卡</p><p>因为要选择Unity Git仓库分支，要展示分支列表，所以这里要先添加<code>Git Parameter</code>，它在 <code>General &gt; 勾选This project is parameterized &gt; 添加参数 &gt; Git Parameter</code>，配置如图：</p><p><img src="/../res/2020-10-19-Mac%E4%B8%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEJenkins%E4%B8%BAUnity%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BAAAR%E3%80%81APK/4.png"></p><blockquote><p>首先要注意若不到<code>Git Parameter</code>选项，可以通过插件包安装，它在<code>首页左侧侧边栏 &gt; Manage Jenkins &gt; Manage Plugins</code>下搜索<code>Git Parameter Plug-In</code>来安装即可，再回来添加<code>Git Parameter</code>既可找到。</p><p>下面的笔记中若是有同样的选项找不到，都可在<code>Manage Plugins</code>搜索安装。</p><p>其次要注意这里 <code>已选仓库</code>  这是用来与Git分支列表和仓库关联，接下来就链接Git仓库。</p></blockquote><p>2、源码管理选项卡</p><p>这里要设置Git参数，它在<code>源码管理 &gt; 选择Multiple SCMs &gt; Git</code>，配置如图：</p><p><img src="/../res/2020-10-19-Mac%E4%B8%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEJenkins%E4%B8%BAUnity%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BAAAR%E3%80%81APK/5.png"></p><p>参数说明：<a href="https://plugins.jenkins.io/git/">https://plugins.jenkins.io/git/</a></p><ol><li><code>Repository URL</code> Git地址。 上一步骤中<code>Git Parameter</code>参数下的<code>已选仓库</code>要与它一致。姑且把它理解为<code>Git Parameter</code>用来把这个<code>Repository URL</code>仓库的分支列表显示出来。</li><li><code>Credentials</code> Git的认证选项。</li><li><code>Check out to a sub-director</code> 源码下载到的指定目录。</li><li><code>Clean before checkout</code> 下拉代码前先清理，比如清理一些编译后的缓存文件。</li><li><code>Advanced clone behaviours</code> 姑且理解为节约下载时间和内存空间。</li></ol><p>3、构建选项卡</p><p>这里要设置Jenkins调用Unity C#代码，需要集成Unity插件<code>Invoke Unity3d Editor</code>，外加一些shll。</p><p><img src="/../res/2020-10-19-Mac%E4%B8%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEJenkins%E4%B8%BAUnity%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BAAAR%E3%80%81APK/6.png"></p><ol><li><code>Invoke Unity3d Editor</code> 选择对应的Unity版本，用Unity命令来调用unityC#，参考这里 <a href="https://plugins.jenkins.io/unity3d-plugin/">unity3d-plugin</a>。</li><li><code>Execite shell</code> 第一段shell脚本利用gradle命令来把导出的Android工程打包成AAR包，参考这里<a href="https://docs.gradle.org/current/userguide/command_line_interface.html">Command-Line Interface</a>。</li><li><code>Execite shell</code> 第二段shell脚本，用于临时测试，把导出的AAR包传输文件服务器上，输入下载地址。</li></ol><blockquote><p>这里需要注意，安装完<code>Invoke Unity3d Editor</code>后，需要配置当前机器上安装的unity路径。它在这里配置<code>首页左侧侧边栏 &gt; Manage Jenkins &gt; Global Tool Configuration</code>下找到<code>Unity3d</code>来配置即可，再回来既可找到对应的版本。</p></blockquote><p>保存，返回到首页，进入到Jenkins项目选择侧边栏<code>Build with Parameters</code>，选择的Unity的Git分支，开始构建，等待结束。<br>到这里Jenkin导出Unity工程AAR就完成了，下面先验证AAR是否可用，再做Jenkins导出apk操作。</p><h2 id="创建一个用于测试的Android工程"><a href="#创建一个用于测试的Android工程" class="headerlink" title="创建一个用于测试的Android工程"></a>创建一个用于测试的Android工程</h2><p>用AndroidStudio创建一个项目，在启动的主Activity中增加一个按钮，点击按钮切换到Unityde Activity。</p><ol><li>将Jenkins导出的AAR拷贝到<code>app/libs</code>下。</li><li>修改app下的<code>build.gradle</code>增加以下代码：</li></ol><figure class="highlight gradle"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gradle"><span class="hljs-keyword">repositories</span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">flatDir</span>&#123;dirs <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;libs&#x27;</span>&#125;&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">dependencies</span> &#123;<br>    .....<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">compile</span> (name:<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;unityLibrary-release&#x27;</span>,ext:<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;aar&#x27;</span>) <span class="hljs-comment">// unityLibrary-release 为aar名称</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至此以及集成完成，下面处理按钮逻辑。</p><ol><li>点击按钮直接从Android原生切换到<code>UnityPlayerActivity</code>。<code>UnityPlayerActivity </code>为AAR中的Activity。不出意外点击按钮直接可以切换到Unity的Activity中。</li><li>从效果图里看到，在Unity的Activity中也切回Android原生，下面有2种方法：<ol><li>自定义Unity Activity入口，这里可以新建一个<code>UnityActivity.Java</code>，继承<code>Activity</code>并且实现<code>IUnityPlayerLifecycleEvents</code>接口。</li><li>还可以新建一个<code>UnityActivity.Java</code>，直接继承AAR中的<code>UnityPlayerActivity</code>.</li></ol></li><li>上面这2种方式都需要新建一个Activity，别忘记XML中对应的配置。这里先选择第2种方式来切换到Unity，下面是2个Activity代码。</li></ol><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">// MainActivity.java</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">MainActivity</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">AppCompatActivity</span> &#123;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">onCreate</span><span class="hljs-params">(Bundle savedInstanceState)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">super</span>.onCreate(savedInstanceState);<br>        setContentView(R.layout.activity_main);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">OnClickChangeUnity</span><span class="hljs-params">(View view)</span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">Intent</span> <span class="hljs-variable">intent</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Intent</span>();<br>        intent.setClass(MainActivity.<span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>, UnityActivity.class);<br>        startActivity(intent);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">// UnityActivity.java</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> com.unity3d.player.UnityPlayerActivity;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">UnityActivity</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">UnityPlayerActivity</span>&#123;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> UnityActivity currentActivity=<span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">onCreate</span><span class="hljs-params">(Bundle savedInstanceState)</span><br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">super</span>.onCreate(savedInstanceState);<br>        currentActivity = <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>;<br>    &#125;<br><br>     <span class="hljs-comment">/** 提供给Unity调用 **/</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">ChangeAndroid</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">Intent</span> <span class="hljs-variable">intent</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Intent</span>();<br>        intent.setClass(UnityActivity.<span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>, MainActivity.class); <br>        startActivity(intent);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行就可以看到开头的效果了，接下来提交Android工程，在回到Jenkins，在利用Jenkins打包apk。</p><h2 id="Jenkins配置自动打包工作流APK"><a href="#Jenkins配置自动打包工作流APK" class="headerlink" title="Jenkins配置自动打包工作流APK"></a>Jenkins配置自动打包工作流APK</h2><p>回到Jenkins，上面Jenkins的有段shll写到临时下载AAR。下面就不手动下载了，改为通过Jenkins的Git操作直接将AAR上传到Android工程，然后在实现打包APK。<br>打开之前配置好的Jenkins工程，选择侧边栏<code>配置</code>。继续修改Jenkins工程。</p><p>1、General选项卡</p><p>添加一个<code>Git Parameter</code>，用来显示Android工程的分支列表，注意<code>已选仓库</code> 要与Andorid Git关联(与前面写的操作一致)。</p><p>2、源码管理选项卡</p><p>添加一个<code>Git</code>，配置好Android工程的Git仓库(与前面写的操作一致)。</p><p>3、构建选项卡 </p><ul><li>添加一个<code>Execute shll</code>，这个shell主要将上面的AAR拷贝到Android的libs下，并将它提交AndroidGit仓库。</li></ul><p><img src="/../res/2020-10-19-Mac%E4%B8%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEJenkins%E4%B8%BAUnity%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BAAAR%E3%80%81APK/7.png"></p><ul><li>在增加一个<code>Execute shll</code>，用于打包安卓APK，先清理上次编译的缓存，利用<code>./gradlew build</code>打包<code>debug</code>、<code>release</code> 2个APK，然后将APK拷贝到FTP服务器上。(<code>gradlew assembleDebu</code> debug包、<code>gradlew assembleRelease</code> release包)</li></ul><p><img src="/../res/2020-10-19-Mac%E4%B8%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEJenkins%E4%B8%BAUnity%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BAAAR%E3%80%81APK/8.png"></p><p>返回执行构建，在日志中就就能看到APK地址输出了。</p><p><img src="/../res/2020-10-19-Mac%E4%B8%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEJenkins%E4%B8%BAUnity%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BAAAR%E3%80%81APK/9.png"></p><h2 id="写在最后"><a href="#写在最后" class="headerlink" title="写在最后"></a>写在最后</h2><ul><li>为了方便测试导出unity工程AAR和Android工程APK的Jenkins流程，将这2步骤放在同一个Jenkins工作流构建。这2步骤是可以分成2个Jenkins工作流来构建，Unity工作流负责导出AAR上传，Android工作流负责下载AAR导出APK。</li><li>Jenkins Git+Shll(或者调用执行本地python)的配合可以完成很多自动化工作流。</li></ul><p>笔记参考文献</p><ol><li><a href="https://www.jenkins.io/zh/doc/">https://www.jenkins.io/zh/doc</a></li><li><a href="https://plugins.jenkins.io/git/">https://plugins.jenkins.io/git</a></li><li><a href="https://plugins.jenkins.io/unity3d-plugin/">https://plugins.jenkins.io/unity3d-plugin</a></li><li><a href="https://docs.gradle.org/current/userguide/command_line_interface.html">Command-Line Interface</a></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
